<div class="row">
  <div class="large-12 columns">
    <div class="coffee-class">
      <h2>Brewed Coffee Class</h2>

      <p>Working from home and weekends shouldn’t mean you have to miss out on
      your morning coffee. Filtered coffee is really simple to make and
      tastes great if you follow a few simple guidelines!</p>

      <p>We will be running <strong>Work From Home Coffee Classes</strong> to teach you the
      basics of making tasty filtered coffee.</p>

      <p>Classes go for <strong>1 hour</strong> and you will learn how to make filtered coffee
      using <strong>French Press</strong>, <strong>Aeropress</strong> and <strong>Pourover</strong> methods.</p>

      <p>Class costs <strong>£15 per person</strong> and there is a maximum of <strong>8 people per
        class</strong>.</p>

      <div style="width:100%; text-align:left;" >
        <iframe src="http://www.eventbrite.com/tickets-external?eid=14045892643&ref=etckt&v=2" frameborder="0" height="256" width="100%" vspace="0" hspace="0" marginheight="5" marginwidth="5" scrolling="auto" allowtransparency="true"></iframe>
      </div>

      <p><em>All of our classes are held at <%= link_to "Curators Coffee Gallery", locations_path %>.<br>
        For details of upcoming classes <%= link_to 'join our waiting list', list_wait_path %>.</em></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

